name: URigVMUnitNode
doc:
The Struct Node represents a Function Invocation of a RIGVM_METHOD
declared on a USTRUCT. Struct Nodes have input / output pins for all
struct UPROPERTY members.

methods.name: GetMethodName
methods.doc: Returns the name of the declared RIGVM_METHOD

methods.name: GetStructDefaultValue
methods.doc: Returns the default value for the struct as text
